  <brief_title>Switch From Oral Iron to Intravenous Ferric Carboxymaltose in Non-dialysis Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Open Label Study to Evaluate Intravenous Ferric Carboxymaltose (Ferinject ®) in Patients With CKD (Pre-dialysis) With Anemia Treated With Epo and Oral Iron in Buenos Aires, Argentina</official_title>
